es the Manor holds? How many can you uncover?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147620/extras/50ef6c078d8cb77325b0a64eb241c9f4.poster.avif?t=1736895520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147620/extras/50ef6c078d8cb77325b0a64eb241c9f4.webm?t=1736895520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147620/extras/50ef6c078d8cb77325b0a64eb241c9f4.mp4?t=1736895520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This 2D point and click game, inspired by titles like Cube Escape, will push your mind and nerves to the limit. Explore an intriguing narrative, atmospheric graphics and complex puzzles as you face the unknown in this thrilling horror game.",
